external_knowledge:
- 'Data treasures' refers to unique data records identified by the 'data_id' column; 
- 'Access footprints' correspond to 'access_count', 'user_name', and 'role';
- 'Evolution milestones' refer to the 'version_number', 'version_date', 'version_description', and 'version_author' of the most accessed data records;
- 'Alarm triggers' are represented by 'alert_count', 'alert_type', and 'alert_message'.
